@Node HARDSOFT "Hard- and Software used while developing"
Most parts of the programs are written in pure Assembler (using the OMA
assembler). Only the lowlevel JPeg functions have been implented
in C (based on the portable C source of the Independent JPeg Group;
This software is based in part on the work of the independent JPeg Group)
and compiled with the MaxonC++ system.

My development system:

Amiga 3000/030/25MHz/18MBRAM/OS3.1
Piccolo SD64(4MB)/EGS7.1
Classical VLab (vlab.library 8.2)
@EndNode
